  "text": "Proof: The lemma is derived from two key observations: (1) at the VMM level, the scheduler can still schedule the domains because their corresponding servers (domains' interfaces) are unchanged; and (2) each server can schedule its own workload because the total resource given to each server is unchanged and only the idle time of C H is utilized by C L . The complete proof can be found in [CITATION_1] .",
